A minimalistic illustration of a descending staircase made of glowing data points and clean geometric lines, each step progressively smaller as it reaches toward a distant horizon. The stairs are rendered in cool teals and warm oranges against a pure white background, with subtle grid lines beneath suggesting a chart axis. Small abstract figures climb down the steps, leaving faint trailing paths behind them. The composition emphasizes negative space and mathematical precision, evoking progress tracking and iterative completion without any text or numbers visible.
